@api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5221

### Fan-out Example 1: Task.WhenAll (all workers run in parallel, results aggregated)
POST {{api_HostAddress}}/api/fanout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workerIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
}

###

### Fan-out Example 1b: Task.WhenAny (returns as soon as the fastest worker finishes)
POST {{api_HostAddress}}/api/fanout/first
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workerIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
}

###

### Fan-out Example 2: Channel-based (enqueue items; background consumers process in parallel)
### Watch the API logs to see 3 consumers picking up items concurrently
POST {{api_HostAddress}}/api/channel/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "count": 9,
  "payload": "hello-world",
  "processingDelayMs": 400
}

###
